<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">先和后除法，计算“加除”、“减除”时，如果两道除法算式的除数相同，可把被除数先相加（或相减），用得到的和（或差）再相除，可使计算简便。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">(187÷17)+(323÷17)=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> (187÷17)+(323÷17)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(187+323)÷17</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=510÷17</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=30</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>